(1) URL HACKING(default value)
    --------------------------
/lightning/o/Opportunity/new?useRecordTypeCheck=1&defaultFieldValues=CloseDate={!TEXT(TODAY())}&backgroundContext=/lightning/o/Opportunity?list?filterName=Recent

NOTE: all thing need to be in text


(#) we can add/remove list button to list view and related list.
    For list view we have to add button to "search layout for salesforce classic" --> List view
